show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/MzenAZ
show.description:
On her anniversary, she was betrayed, discarded, and humiliated—until the truth shattered their illusion. They thought she was nothing, but she was the heiress behind everything they owned.
Now reborn with power, wealth, and a dangerous ally, she’s back to turn the tables—for good.
